 Cookbook<\/em> or the <em>Everyday Cookbook<\/em> for the Vegetable stock paste recipe.","Refrigerate or freeze any leftovers to enjoy later.","Crush some <em>Curried almonds<\/em> in your Thermomix to garnish your soup for added texture and spice.","Store leftover curry powder in a cool, dark place.","The cashew nuts in this recipe add creaminess to the soup without the need for dairy."],"basicInfo":["easy","5m","20m","2 portions"]}